Ok i just don't understand this, somone mentioned it in another post and i just don't get it.  You have the entire Plane to clear, for planes like Hate, once the bottom is cleared you can start working on the 2nd floor that much sooner.<br>
<br>
I see so many times people getting bent about a 2nd party showing up in the planes, why?  Is sharing that hard?  The first group there, gets camp preferance, the 2nd group has to find someplace else to pull to.  <br>
<br>
I can see if the 2nd group trained you and got you killed, yeah that would suck, but getting bent about sharing an entire  zone, i just don't understand.<br>
<br>
